	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That connector should work fine with any SNES produced in 1995 or later (in the US at least). IIRC that would include the last pcb revision of the SNES and the SNES "mini".
<br />Of course, it could be used with all SNES units as long as you desolder the connector.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
